description:
######## 50% OFF #########
•	Chinups are the, one of the best exercise for muscles of the chest, arms and core development. 
•	If you're very serious about increasing your strength, follow this six week training program and you'll be on your way to completing 20 consecutive chinups!
•	Chinups are important and best Chest Exercise.
•	With only 30 minutes per week, this app is going to help you get fit and do 20 chinups.
•	Perform an initial test first & then this number will dictate your targets over the ensuing six week period.
•	This app also helps you to decide the target by performing an initial test.
•	If you are following the training program strictly you can perform 20 chinups.
•	You can definitely gain strength using this application & performing the training program.
Features: 
•	Ideal app for gaining the strength. 
•	Predefined 6 week program, so you no need to remember schedule.
•	Predefined timer defined in this for taking rest.
•	Initial test will decided your schedule on 6 week programmer.
